603
00:57:38,246 --> 00:57:42,500 
<i>Now in Contagem,</i>
<i>it's 2:20 p.m. of a new day!</i>

604
00:57:42,584 --> 00:57:47,130 
<i>What a joy it is to experience</i>
<i>a new sunrise!</i>

605
00:57:47,213 --> 00:57:51,301 
<i>If you're out there feeling lost,</i>
<i>not knowing where to go,</i>

606
00:57:51,384 --> 00:57:54,512 
<i>I wish you luck in a brand-new day.</i>

607
00:57:54,596 --> 00:57:58,766 
<i>May it come full of smiles</i>
<i>and hope in your path.</i>

608
00:57:59,017 --> 00:58:04,022 
<i>May the sun light up your life</i>
<i>and God bless your encounters.</i>

609
00:58:04,481 --> 00:58:08,151 
